### Why Code.org?
- Our physical computing unit allows students to make an app connected to their device, rather than coding a device disconnected from the screen.
- This unit is connected to Code.org's App Lab, so you can use all of your favorite App Lab features (like databases and graphics) with the physical computing device!

### Professional learning
This self-paced online unit is intended as an 150-minute introduction to our optional unit on physical computing.

Through completing this online unit, participants will:

- Get an introduction to Physical Computing.
- Practice key concepts included in the unit.
- Engage with the maker app.
- Explore end of chapter projects.

